  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To examine the impact of using 2 validated PROMs during the care of an orthopaedic condition
      on shared decision making, patient centered care, and patient outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Not yet recruiting</overall_status>
